<p><b>Thomas Bernhard</b> (born <b>Nicolaas Thomas Bernhard</b>, 9 February 1931 – 12 February 1989) was an <a href="/wiki/Austria" title="Austria">Austrian</a> <a href="/wiki/Playwright" title="Playwright">playwright</a> and <a href="/wiki/Novelist" title="Novelist" class="mw-redirect">novelist</a>.</p>
